Paper: hep-th/9708021

Date: 1997-08-05

Title: On the Schild action for D=0 and D=1 strings

Authors: Oleg A. Soloviev (Queen Mary College)

Comments: 12pp, latex file. Minor corrections

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A13 (1998) 2415-2426

It is shown that the integration measure over the matrix $Y$ in the matrixrepresentation of the Schild action can be fixed by comparing the Schild matrixmodel with the random lattice string model for D=0. It is further checked thatthe given measure is consistent with the case D=1 as well.